## [FAIL] LOW — E5 smoke test missing blank-slide regression case

The E5 visual smoke test list does not include: "Item with `imageCount > 0`, non-empty lead, and zero body-content blocks → carousel should contain exactly 1 slide (the grid-cover), no blank trailing slide."

Without this test scenario in E5, the HIGH gap #3 (grid-alone-guard) would produce a blank slide that goes unnoticed in smoke testing unless the tester happens to use such an item.

