## Verdict

**NEEDS WORK**

Three HIGH findings that will produce Codex R1 findings:
1. `projectAutoBlocksToSlides` budget-fix missing → DK-6 editor/renderer divergence, `leadHeightPx` disposition contradiction
2. TypeScript error in A4b `dataUrls` fallback → `tsc --noEmit` hard fail (Code Quality Gate)
3. Grid-alone-guard blank-slide regression → untested, affects real items with grid+lead+no-body

Fix gaps 1–3 before Generator phase. Gaps 4–5 are MEDIUM/LOW and can be addressed in-spec or caught by Generator review.
